       _D_f  gives  a summary of disk usage on ms-dos system.  Spe-
       cial care was taken to  specify  joined  drives,  and  not
       abort  on the floppy disk driver when a floppy disk is not
       present.

       Specifying no options will show the format  of  your  hard
       disk  when  you use join (which I do).  Each hard disk can
       have 1 main paritition and 1 extended partition, which can
       be  4  dos disks.  So you can have a total of 5 dos drives
       on each hard disk.  I  use  join,  it  can  be  confusing.
       Don't  believe  the  sizes about removable media, it isn't
       always right and I didn't try to understand DOS's strategy
       for this.

